dataset.title: The first species of Eutheimorphus Franz & Löbl in Thailand (Coleoptera, Staphylinidae, Scydmaeninae)

abstract.para: This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Jałoszyński, Paweł (2023): The first species of Eutheimorphus Franz & Löbl in Thailand (Coleoptera, Staphylinidae, Scydmaeninae). Zootaxa 5323 (3): 435-439, DOI: 10.11646/zootaxa.5323.3.8, URL: http://dx.doi.org/10.11646/zootaxa.5323.3.8
